{"tid":555943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台狗只識以怨報德","createTime":"2018-02-10T04:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T06:43:41.000Z","uid":11779,"like":30,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d52608db96ab34b3023253ab41978d734745510","tid":555943,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"之前有個痴線佬係地鐵放火燒傷個台灣女遊客，就算唔關港鐵事， 港鐵都比左幾十萬慰問金（其實又咪係我地埋單）班台狗一句多謝都冇. <br />\n平時台灣全完唔理啲危樓 明知間酒店頂唔到地震都唔理 搞到累死左對香港夫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好話賠償 班台灣連一句慰問都冇，淨係識用日本黎打J 仲日日笑鳩香港人比支那統治.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台狗都支那根本一撚榚 都係畜牲黎."},{"pid":"e3dcb1aa0dd8ba5b4a09076fdf74f1fde819b7c0","tid":555943,"uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"睇見台灣地震就好撚心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9471d4d8ae85bfe558059d7bb6203f343c7f60ca","tid":555943,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3dcb1aa0dd8ba5b4a09076fdf74f1fde819b7c0","tid":555943,"uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"睇見台灣地震就好撚心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a8ae587b11f606d67b97f380ad8a1aab795ae1","tid":555943,"uid":11779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9471d4d8ae85bfe558059d7bb6203f343c7f60ca","tid":555943,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3dcb1aa0dd8ba5b4a09076fdf74f1fde819b7c0","tid":555943,"uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"睇見台灣地震就好撚心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=